title: Congressional reception attendees at the White House | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




April 23, 2009

 



Congressional reception attendees at the White House




THE WHITE HOUSE   Office of the Press Secretary  __________________________________________________________________  FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE                                         April 23, 2009  Below is a list of bipartisan members of Congress attending tonight’s reception at the White House:   Rep. David Loebsack (D-IA)  Rep. Mary Bono Mack (R-CA)  Rep. Doris Matsui (D-CA)  Rep. Jerry McNerney (D-CA)  Rep. Ed Perlmutter (D-CO)  Rep. Chellie Pingree (D-ME)  Rep. Adam Schiff (D-CA)  Rep.
